TileCollection.title: 500-1000 kWh (5.1¢)  1000-2000 kWh (8.6¢) Above 2000 kWh (10.4¢)
TileCollection.Remarks: Many electric companies require that you use a minimum amount of electricity each month. Our shopping tool allows you to see if a company requires a minimum electricity usage and if there is an associated fee or credit. Note: These fees or credits are already included in the average kWh prices and are not in addition to or taken off the top of the amounts posted.
